 />\n當納粹逮捕猶太人時，我沒有說話，因為我不是猶太人。<br />\n<br />\n他們逮捕我時，沒有任何一個人可以抗議。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T08:10:54.000Z","msg":"當納粹逮捕共產黨員時，你說話了<br />\n共產黨來殺你全家時，已經没有人可以說話了"},{"pid":"d709860a2aa7f904f214addf81911f7808769985","tid":1443218,"uid":154433,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T08:13:26.000Z","msg":"same old trick used by Communist Party"},{"pid":"fa85e912c6dc60b311f998118294b9c4705fb42d","tid":1443218,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:11:00.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"eb33837dedf65af8fadb6cc924ded693f0b8d6cb","tid":1443218,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:44:30.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"8bcd5f111018f613b291c9f7ee6934f040e3de2b","tid":1443218,"uid":35262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:47:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4e18aecd5b7f4829f98194b477fcf29ea0228a98","tid":1443218,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:29:14.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"a7a55bac3184c5bf92bdb71f85cec32d173f21ad","tid":1443218,"uid":305009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:31:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支共最識玩"},{"pid":"024f678500b820d8b4c3958d121ccad27a5ae03c","tid":1443218,"uid":301152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:57:16.000Z","msg":"有黨性冇人性"},{"pid":"a0bad2750bdea35eb9ac6cc81c254545e9f196ab","tid":1443218,"uid":146055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8ce23f1c7e607d2deb42530800ca6b8a715787f","tid":1443218,"uid":2419,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T07:14:26.000Z","msg":"繼續話人搞事啦 屌你老母藍絲狗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:58:50.000Z","msg":"個班人真係仆街冚家剷死<br />\n唔燒到埋身佢哋都唔會知驚"},{"pid":"b4e2a7d5a7f1aa9cd8697eb5de5c558accd1f4f9","tid":1443218,